      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 Chart1 上图例项一的图例标示的宽度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Legend</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">LegendEntries</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">LegendKey</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Width</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例显示 Sheet1 中的第一个图表的第二个图例项的图例标示的高度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> legend = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Legend</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(legend.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">LegendEntries</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">LegendKey</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Height</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
